{
  "stem": "3933.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I-- I went into the car-- to the-- to the train-- goes to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Lwow is a very big city in Poland. 'Luh-VOOV,' called, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Lwow. 'Lemberg,' in German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This is a city where there were universities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We used to hear of this city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I never been there, but I heard, and I figure-- And I also hear something about the Polish committee.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There is lots of Polish refugees-- goyim-- Gentile.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were killed from the Ukrainian [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You see, you've got to know-- to understand all this-- The Ukrainians were with-- working with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They became squealers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They became cooperating with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they hated the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] are Polish Catholics.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were-- they were going around killing not Jews but the Polacks from the small cities, and they were refugees going there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I attach myself to those Polish refugees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Was a very good idea, in fact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I didn't look-- but I didn't have ID-- you've got to have a-- a birth certificate, a passport, or something, and I never got anything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Then I arrived in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I came to Lwow by myself, with my son, first of all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Before I find this Jewish-- this Polish center.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I will never forget-- I-- we went to a park.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was a beautiful day in a Sunday-- people coming from church.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I went in a park and fall right away asleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "My son right away asleep in a sitting park.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I let him sleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "After this, I looked around the beautiful buildings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to a place in the early morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I waited a little while, because it was too early.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knocked the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A woman came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, oh, who are you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Polish.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
